<title>CHINA: China sewage treatment plant explodes, kills 12.</title>
<headline>China sewage treatment plant explodes, kills 12.</headline>
<dateline>SHANGHAI 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>An explosion and fire at a chemical factory's sewage treatment plant in the central China city of Chongqing killed 12 people, a plant official said on Thursday.</p>
<p>Six people were hurt by the explosion on May 4 in the Changshu Chemical Plant, the official said.</p>
<p>&quot;We are investigating what caused the explosion,&quot; he said. &quot;Some of the raw materials we use are flammable and explosive, but we cannot reach any conclusions before careful investigation.&quot;</p>
<p>The official declined to give further details.</p>
